Write a program to print given number is Even or Odd.

import java.util.*;
class Even
{
	public static void main(String args[])
	{
		int x;
		Scanner in=new Scanner(System.in);
		System.out.print("Enter x value");
		x=in.nextInt();
		if(x%2==0)
		{
		System.out.print("Given number is Even");
		}
		else
		{
		System.out.print("Given number is odd");
		}
	}
}

Output:
D:\>javac Even.java
D:\>java Even
Enter x value 123
Given number is odd

D:\>javac Even.java
D:\>java Even
Enter x value 648
Given number is Even
